  "text": "This section gives a brief overview of the main existing resolution-based calculi for QBF. Q-resolution (Q-Res), by Kleine Büning et al. [CITATION_1] , is a resolution-like calculus that operates on QBFs in prenex form where the matrix is a CNF. The rules are given in Figure 1 . Long-distance resolution (LD-Q-Res) appears",
